{"tid":1106080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲總理選舉造勢 誤用中文向韓裔選民打招呼　","createTime":"2019-04-14T10:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T11:42:28.000Z","uid":28765,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6faa820ba1cc569f2c7b14b5f34dcbbc5e1c015a","tid":1106080,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190414/photo/bkn-20190414180224988-0414_00912_001_01p.jpg?20190414181033\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190414%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190414180224988-0414_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20190414181033&h=cef19f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子（左）解釋自己是韓裔人。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總理講中文打招呼　女選民尷尬答：我是韓裔<br />\n0:00/0:08<br />\n<br />\n澳洲總理莫里森昨日（13日）到悉尼街頭為即將到來的大選造勢，他與一名亞裔女子打招呼時，用中文說「你好」，但對方立即稱：「不，我是韓裔人。」場面異常尷尬。 <br />\n<br />\n莫里森當日在拉票大會後，帶妻子到悉尼西區史卓菲參觀，有30多名記者跟隨。他在一間滿是韓裔及華裔的韓國餐廳親手學煮菜，又到街上接觸選民。莫里森與其中一名亞裔女子握手，並說「你好（Ni hao）」，但對方糾正稱：「不，不，不，我是韓裔人（裔）。」 <br />\n<br />\n對於被總理誤認為華人，女子事後對記者笑稱並不介意，但網民的批評排山倒海。有網民稱：「史卓菲的韓裔人非常多，基本上每個做生意的都是韓裔人。假定他們都是華人是種族主義，非常愚蠢。」有人批評莫里森總是說錯話，人們不應投票給他。又有人諷道：「華人和韓裔人對他來說看起來都一個樣。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190414/mobile/bkn-20190414180224988-0414_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190414%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190414180224988-0414_00912_001.html&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=14cb8630\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190414/mobile/bkn-20190414180224988-0414_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ef001825e17fcc5a5b2ff4c942a3b31623e34325","tid":1106080,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:14:39.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e3220c06d678d49d2917d0e4723c7fb2c90ae9","tid":1106080,"uid":132038,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca4a4bfa9009206fd8e11f140bf58a5a774ee3cd","tid":1106080,"uid":66245,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:19:24.000Z","msg":"They all look the same<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1ae4e82c5c06468f21e3cbfac18a708c0c422e","tid":1106080,"uid":156121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:22:12.000Z","msg":"蠢過鳩屎"},{"pid":"5bb7999826637009ae92c165fa1fcbed300bcfee","tid":1106080,"uid":8543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:22:26.000Z","msg":"韓國人一定係中國人"},{"pid":"bb4880ca9349a9184f813f43191d220c1ed58395","tid":1106080,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef001825e17fcc5a5b2ff4c942a3b31623e34325","tid":1106080,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:14:39.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:22:32.000Z","msg":"你user名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b6ed3e7f1cca6e133c7e1620095f6fdaa45469","tid":1106080,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298265f7eacbc1ac08d749daf71ef9a06ee0c8cc","tid":1106080,"uid":191762,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:30:43.000Z","msg":"話你中國人咪仲好<br />\n韓國人喺外國全部都做雞嘅"},{"pid":"40156e9128c748bb8fe67209c6c5c3d99aec0911","tid":1106080,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:39:29.000Z","msg":"Strathfield 個火車站，得幾隻白人，其他全部韓國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92a4d531c55ef4fd12212a07da4a35e56b1be99","tid":1106080,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r